          Explore AI automation, QA engineering, and next-gen productivity with cutting-edge tech.
        </p>
        <a href="#ai-use-cases" class="mt-6 inline-block text-blue-600 font-semibold hover:underline transition" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">↓ Explore Use Cases</a>
